1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:03,109
This walkthrough connects the whole QualCanvas workflow.

2
00:00:03,109 --> 00:00:07,435
The exact method belongs to your study, but the practical

3
00:00:07,435 --> 00:00:11,762
sequence is consistent: set up carefully, keep evidence visible and

4
00:00:11,762 --> 00:00:15,656
document the decisions that turn coding into an argument.

5
00:00:16,056 --> 00:00:21,019
Create a canvas with a name that identifies the study and phase.

6
00:00:21,019 --> 00:00:25,155
Begin blank or use a methodology template, then adapt every

7
00:00:25,155 --> 00:00:28,464
starting code or question to the actual protocol.

8
00:00:28,864 --> 00:00:35,450
Add transcripts or other supported sources using clear, non-identifying titles where appropriate.

9
00:00:35,450 --> 00:00:41,488
Verify each import and keep a source inventory before analysis expands.

10
00:00:41,888 --> 00:00:46,268
Read each passage in context, apply a code that answers

11
00:00:46,268 --> 00:00:50,648
the research question and compare new examples with earlier ones.

12
00:00:50,648 --> 00:00:54,152
Refine the codebook when meanings drift or overlap.

13
00:00:54,552 --> 00:00:59,517
Use text, coding or framework tools to locate patterns and exceptions.

14
00:00:59,517 --> 00:01:04,031
Treat every output as a route back to the material,

15
00:01:04,031 --> 00:01:06,288
not as an automatic finding.

16
00:01:06,688 --> 00:01:09,928
Write memos as the interpretation develops.

17
00:01:09,928 --> 00:01:15,328
Link claims to evidence, note alternative explanations and record why

18
00:01:15,328 --> 00:01:18,568
a code, case or theme changed.

19
00:01:18,968 --> 00:01:22,554
For team coding, inspect agreement and disagreements.

20
00:01:22,554 --> 00:01:27,677
For every study, review the codebook, ethics boundaries and analytical

21
00:01:27,677 --> 00:01:32,288
trail before describing the process in a methods section.

22
00:01:32,688 --> 00:01:37,703
Export the report, codebook, workbook, visual or exchange file that

23
00:01:37,703 --> 00:01:39,709
the next step requires.

24
00:01:39,709 --> 00:01:44,724
Verify the result, protect the downloaded copy and keep the

25
00:01:44,724 --> 00:01:47,232
original project available for trace-back.

26
00:01:47,632 --> 00:01:52,209
The value of the workflow is the visible chain from

27
00:01:52,209 --> 00:01:55,413
source to code, pattern, memo and claim.

28
00:01:55,413 --> 00:02:00,448
QualCanvas organises that chain; the researcher remains responsible for its meaning.
